london     ipa     is the  capital  and largest urban area of  england  and the  united kingdom  at its core the ancient  city of london  to which the name historically belongs still retains its limited mediaeval boundaries but since at least the 19th century the name london has also referred to the whole metropolis which has developed around it today the bulk of this conurbation forms the london  region of england  and the  greater london  administrative area with its own elected mayor and assembly
